1) To create a project in angular use the following command line
in node.js
*---------npm install -g @angular/cli---------*
2) Verify the version of angular
*---------ng --version---------*
3) create angular project. create it in a folder ley say UI
*---------ng new appName(we nnpmame ours angular10)---------*
4) skip the routing featuer it will be done latter
5)Run the project 
*---------ng serve --open ---------*
5) create a component
*---------ng generate component componentName ---------*
6) create a child component
*---------ng generate component componentName/componentName ---------*
7) create a services
a services a code to perform somthing and in whcih it can be resused. no need to code it again
*---------ng generate service serviceName ---------*
8)import your service in to module and add the service name in provider :[servicesName]

9) complete the code in share.service file so that we can consume all the api methode
    -import {HttpClientModule} from '@angular/common/http';
    -import {FormsModule,ReactiveFormsModule} from '@angular/forms';
    -imports: [
    HttpClientModule,
    FormsModule,
    ReactiveFormsModule
  ],
10) routing is navigating to a partigular screen using url  


___________________ANGULAT DIRACTORY_________________________________
**package.json**: it conatin all the packages, modeul or dependency
    need for this project
**angular.json**: conatain all the configuration  option, for serving, testing and buildin =g this progect

**index.html**: it is the file which get render when runing the app

**app.module.ts**: is is an entry or a way to import all the modules, new component or services we created in the angular progetect

**app.component calles app** is the root component. we can add any number of child components. all of them will reside in tis folder app

**app.component.html**it is the html containt of the root component

**app.component.ts**it contain all the functionalities writen in typescript or js. these functionalities will be used by **app.component.html**

**app.component.css**contain all the styling need for our app.component.html

**style.css**contain all the styling need to be apply to all component